author: Shayla Love, Kate Lowenstein
title: Warm Water, Garlic, Essential Oils: They Won't Protect You From Coronavirus
description: As COVID-19 misinformation runs rampant, pseudoscience expert Tim Caulfield has been tasked with keeping track of all the bunk.
